                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18381126-name-812" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18381126-name-812" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18381126-name-812" type="surname" value="CURTIS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18381126-name-812" type="given" value="DENNIS"></interp>DENNIS CURTIS</persName>
                  </hi>. I live with Mr. Barnet Manning Collins and his partner. On the 1st of November a gentleman came to the shop and priced some things—he asked to look at a coat—I went to show him one, and it was gone—I went down Wild-street, and saw the prisoner with the coat on—I followed him, and saw the ticket on it—I seized him-here is the shop mark on it—I am thirteen years old.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
